Title: service details view: unable to render view due to long filename
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1677857283
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

Some service details views displayed an error with a crash report reading the
message "OSError ((36, 'File name too long'))". This was for example the case
when configuring a long commandline with the "Integrate Nagios plugins" rule.
This has been fixed.

